title: BRIEF-Enwave Signs Commercial Royalty-Bearing License Agreement With Nomad Nutrition
text: February 26, 2018 / 2:12 PM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-Enwave Signs Commercial Royalty-Bearing License Agreement With Nomad Nutrition Reuters Staff 1 Min Read Feb 26 (Reuters) - Enwave Corp: * ENWAVE SIGNS COMMERCIAL ROYALTY-BEARING LICENSE AGREEMENT WITH NOMAD NUTRITION LIMITED TO PRODUCE READY-TO-EAT MEALS IN CANADA, RECEIVES PURCHASE ORDER FOR RADIANT ENERGY VACUUM MACHINERY * NOMAD TO PAY CO UNDISCLOSED ROYALTY ON REVENUE FROM SALES OF PRODUCTS IN EXCHANGE FOR RIGHT TO MANUFACTURE SPECIFIC PRODUCTS IN CANADA Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
